	* Makefile (CFLAGS-ftrylockfile.c): Add -D_IO_MTSAFE_IO.

	* cleanup.c: Move declarations of _GI_pthread_cleanup_push and
	_GI_pthread_cleanup_pop to pthreadP.h.

